Text:
All perfect praise be to the flying spaghetti monster, The Lord of the Worlds.  I testify that
there is none worthy of worship except flying spaghetti monster,and that Hamburgler  is His
slave and Messenger, may flying spaghetti monster exalt his mention as well as that of his
family and all his companions.

        Benifits Of Honey In Medicine That retards Said That 1400 Years Ago
